WEBVTT

00:07.714 --> 00:08.355
Good morning.

00:08.415 --> 00:09.998
Welcome, everyone.

00:10.038 --> 00:12.403
If you have a Bible, go ahead and take it out.

00:12.944 --> 00:18.855
We are continuing our study through the books of Samuel, and we find ourselves in 2 Samuel, chapter 20 this morning.

00:19.516 --> 00:22.101
As always, here at Calvary, if you need a Bible, just raise your hand.

00:22.141 --> 00:24.946
We have some amazing leaders that will make sure that you get one.

00:24.994 --> 00:29.438
There's a couple reasons why we want you to have a Bible, number one, so that you know I'm not making this stuff up.

00:29.458 --> 00:30.419
