00:31.120 --> 00:33.122
But we believe this has the power to change your life.

00:33.222 --> 00:38.887
Seeing the gospel on the pages of scripture has transformed my life in ways that I can't even begin to tell you.

00:39.308 --> 00:42.651
And so we want you to have a Bible for yourself so you can see the words on the pages.

00:43.051 --> 00:46.354
Like Pastor John said, my name is Jav and I get to serve at our Boca campus.

00:46.454 --> 00:49.257
It's an honor to get to be here today and open the Word of God with you.

00:49.277 --> 00:54.642
I was reminded this week of a quote from the great Alistair bag when he said, the Word of God

00:54.722 --> 00:58.267
does the work of God through the Spirit of God in the people of God.

00:58.768 --> 00:59.449
That's why we're here.

00:59.569 --> 01:05.357
Every time we gather as a church, we open up this book, we read these stories and the Lord speaks to us.

01:05.397 --> 01:08.962
